com.esri.mo2.map.img
Interface ImageCatalog

All Superinterfaces:
Dataset, GeoDataset, ImageClass, MapDataset, Searchable
All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseImageDirectoryCatalog
public interface ImageCatalog
extends ImageClass

An ImageCatalog is a kind of ImageClass that obtains imagery from one or more ImageFiles that are defined within some container object that is implementation-dependent. For example, the container for the BaseImageDirectoryCatalog class is a file system directory.
